{"tid":184600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(集氣 ! )  [救救港豬] Save Hong Kong Pigs 正式成立！","createTime":"2017-04-03T02:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T23:41:32.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf869faa2cebd72b06e17d81deb9a22ced0a14f","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">About:</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們每日去<strong>港鐵</strong>，目擊港豬被送去辦公室<strong>奴役</strong>既過程。港豬跟你老細個仔一樣聰明，能夠感受痛楚同疲憊，唔應該被視為<strong>奴隸</strong>。（btw我地唔係傻架）<br />\n<br />\nWe are a love based labour rights organization. We organise regular vigils in MTR and bear witness to the Kong Pigs as they are sent to offices."},{"pid":"8254a04dcc32593bbd3e8643eb0f5efb0c05e1dc","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 16 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/x/ties-shop-21548572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.dreamstime.com%2Fx%2Fties-shop-21548572.jpg&h=3e4af81a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思。呢D繩用泥綁乜嘢？<br />\n@香港商場<br />\n.<br />\nExcuse me, what, or, WHO, you're gonna tie on these."},{"pid":"a9c134b78544ede3292e8e936aa12045ec0efdac","tid":184600,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:33:20.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee0bfa04e9f71905e44e027ea6d68742f7815a0","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 16 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c31WmH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc31WmH6.jpg&h=c3495922&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地成日將「方便」放在口邊。原來「方便」係咁既樣既。。。源頭就係你要手到拿來。<br />\n<br />\n夜晚、紅日無得開戶口炒股好唔方便，唔通對佢黎講，呢種生活就好方便？"},{"pid":"ddaa30c2806c11430be359d101bdc42ba9b9cab9","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 19 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好話支持但自己唔黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n.<br />\n接近9點是港豬們被奴役的時候。即使我們不能就牠們，也必須至少目睹為我們的「樓價」、「競爭力」、「GDP」而犧牲的牠們。好多人食花生，默默地自己吃花生，但港豬不想你默默的默默的，牠們想要你發聲！！<br />\n<br />\n22/2（三）<br />\n845AM<br />\n中環地鐵站D出口<br />\n.<br />\nIn a million year, DONT BE A SILENT VEGAN. Kong Pigs DO NOT want you to be silent. They DEMAND voicing for them.<br />\n.<br />\nMorning Vigil<br />\nCentral MTR exit D<br />\n8:45 AM<br />\n<br />\n#witnessing, #documenting, #banner holding, #candle lighting"},{"pid":"592a85dc224d974ca251d127f0ad4287fb070d03","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 21 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/pictures/photo/BJ20130306094756/02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Fpictures%2Fphoto%2FBJ20130306094756%2F02.jpg&h=0498bb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日10點係港豬們被奴役一刻。請來在中環街頭目擊。我們站、感受、同在，已經賦予活動意義。<br />\n.<br />\n845AM@中環地鐵站D出口 集合<br />\n.<br />\nI don't understand."},{"pid":"4006de735e2a76bef3efe28a1718ad6a335a1fba","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 23 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集中營。<br />\n售樓處裡面全部都係殺人既兇器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nConcentration Camp. Inside it's All tools for murdering. God bless humanity.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170114/large/1484365713_2abf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170114%2Flarge%2F1484365713_2abf.jpg&h=fc0211d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6d9223d14d6f4a3c52c7f5bd98f2bf90a780dda","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T02:52:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 23 February &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中環國金。<br />\n<br />\n邊度半夜會咁光？咁光因為仲未收得工。<br />\n@中環國金<br />\nGod bless the Kong pigs in our empty tummies<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> They need our voice...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VSf59Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VSf59Q.jpg&h=9f11ffaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caed02cd6b969f58aeda1c34fe0fff154deb451b","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:23:36.000Z","msg":"有無人支持"},{"pid":"572cd855c2833e391bc89d120780dcb3a1fb5169","tid":184600,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"fca655a69d2f21c51bb6ab07374e8db7f7f96e7f","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有</blockquote><br />\n參唔參加一人一心心既救救港豬大行動？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請拎起你既鍵盤，投下神聖既心心"},{"pid":"37285a5ae4513caf85c141e317bbf90d3e88965b","tid":184600,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有</blockquote><br />\n參唔參加一人一心心既救救港豬大行動？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請拎起你既鍵盤，投下神聖既心心</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04223c22f9006bbeb8527c58b36d363aef29bc30","tid":184600,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643390b8103c1b17cd09d0889adf78fe3dfbb9b9","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:38:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b342bdf186286e36bbb10409ee5ff1a1816aaef","tid":184600,"uid":40624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a615037f5e9db62c603da58b55554520bff5ba","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請支持本網頁。認同請分享。"},{"pid":"52dd05dfaf420170217a6f456da612303af4e0de","tid":184600,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"強貼留名"},{"pid":"2a7092645ea780cd21b1b97302493ec9b686f778","tid":184600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"455677fee2bd9d34f74e1e402ffc74e3def2acc2","tid":184600,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e67a8f02fa556dc8396b9ccdf300df1a171ca18","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>救救港豬 Save Hong Kong Pigs</strong></span><br />\n&middot; 11 March &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「救救港豬」行動到鐵港鐵站目送一車車港豬自動送入甲級商廈，反思人生的意義。本地勞動豬隻超過390萬，未計(假)自僱人士，香港人每日工時超過60/星期。為左香港人既「競爭力」，呢D時間白白被犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n辦公室一般都設在遠離上車盤的地方，使港豬的血肉之軀要坐起碼個幾兩個鐘港鐵先返到屋企。港鐵站外面目送港豬們由列車送上商廈，是我們能夠做到最少的事情。如果被奴役的對象變成老細個仔、老細二奶或其他老細的屋企人，老細會有不一樣的反應嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如果你是廢青，希望你透過參與行動為港豬大力發聲。如果你不是廢青，歡迎一齊參加，尋找港豬奴役之路。<br />\n<br />\n「守護港豬」行動內容：<br />\n-集合後步行至港鐵站口<br />\n-簡介港豬從填鴨教育至爭政府十幾萬學債的經歷<br />\n-等候港豬列車<br />\n-目送港豬們被送入商廈<br />\n-拍照/錄影過程<br />\n-參加者可使已準備的橫額<br />\n-透過VR技術體驗辦公室及納米式新樓盤的環境<br />\n<br />\n我們明白單憑目送港豬們被送入辦公室並不能使牠們免於被奴役，但我們相信牠們在死前送牠們離開世界，以及在社交媒體為港豬發聲，使更多人關注到服務性奴隸的權益，反思企業家背後對其他生命的不平等。<br />\n<br />\n我們盡量避免與保安職員發生衝突，以和平態度目送港豬們，在社交媒體分享相片影片紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJK8m1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJK8m1S.jpg&h=2ede706f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40ef4d05e3271f5aa38c1299aa576e93c7f5c156","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327975489127de76a8f98148f335fef64974339a","tid":184600,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎住幅畫望住人地死仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff30d1f86430eef7bdc7ed7182489223c13262f","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎住幅畫望住人地死仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地覺得好有意義。"},{"pid":"77eb5b984b85ab6b67e384d7c6e3ae4845588a81","tid":184600,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T23:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}